#: sunshine-cloud-storage/includes/hooks.php:316
msgid ""
"WP Offload Media plugin is currently active. These two plugins should not be "
"active at the same time as they will conflict. Please deactivate WP Offload "
"Media before using Sunshine Cloud Storage."
msgstr ""
"De WP Offload Media-plug-in is momenteel actief. Deze twee plug-ins mogen "
"niet tegelijkertijd actief zijn, omdat ze met elkaar conflicteren. "
"Deactiveer WP Offload Media voordat u Sunshine Cloud Storage gebruikt."

#: sunshine-cloud-storage/includes/hooks.php:318
msgid ""
"<strong>Good news:</strong> Sunshine Cloud Storage can work with your items "
"previously offloaded via WP Offload Media. After deactivating WP Offload "
"Media, your existing offloaded images will continue to work automatically - "
"no migration required."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Goed nieuws:</strong> Sunshine Cloud Storage werkt met uw items die "
"eerder via WP Offload Media zijn gedownload. Nadat u WP Offload Media hebt "
"gedeactiveerd, blijven uw bestaande gedownloade afbeeldingen automatisch "
"werken. Migratie is niet nodig."

#: sunshine-cloud-storage/includes/hooks.php:323
msgid ""
"<strong>Sunshine Cloud Storage:</strong> WP Offload Media plugin is active. "
"You have Cloud Storage set to \"Entire WordPress site\" which may conflict. "
"Consider setting it to \"Sunshine galleries only\" or disabling one of the "
"plugins."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Sunshine Cloud Storage:</strong> De WP Offload Media-plug-in is "
"actief. Je hebt Cloud Storage ingesteld op \"Hele WordPress-site\", wat "
"conflicten kan veroorzaken. Overweeg om dit in te stellen op \"Alleen "
"Sunshine-galerijen\" of een van de plug-ins uit te schakelen."

#: sunshine-cloud-storage/includes/hooks.php:345
msgid ""
"Your cloud storage bucket does not support per-object ACLs (Access Control "
"Lists). This means Sunshine cannot set individual files as public or "
"private, which may cause thumbnails to not display or full-resolution images "
"to be publicly accessible."
msgstr ""
"Uw cloudopslagbucket ondersteunt geen ACL's (Access Control Lists) per "
"object. Dit betekent dat Sunshine individuele bestanden niet als openbaar of "
"privé kan instellen, waardoor miniaturen mogelijk niet worden weergegeven of "
"afbeeldingen met volledige resolutie openbaar toegankelijk zijn."

#: sunshine-cloud-storage/includes/hooks.php:349
msgid ""
"<strong>How to fix:</strong> Go to Google Cloud Console &rarr; Cloud Storage "
"&rarr; Your Bucket &rarr; Permissions &rarr; Access Control &rarr; Switch "
"from \"Uniform\" to \"Fine-grained\"."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Oplossing:</strong> Ga naar Google Cloud Console → Cloud Storage → "
"Uw bucket → Machtigingen → Toegangscontrole → Schakel over van 'Uniform' "
"naar 'Fijnmazig'."

#: sunshine-cloud-storage/includes/hooks.php:351
msgid ""
"<strong>How to fix:</strong> Go to S3 Console &rarr; Your Bucket &rarr; "
"Permissions &rarr; Object Ownership &rarr; Edit &rarr; Select \"ACLs "
"enabled\" with \"Bucket owner preferred\"."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Oplossing:</strong> Ga naar S3 Console → Uw bucket → Machtigingen → "
"Objectbezit → Bewerken → Selecteer \"ACL's ingeschakeld\" met "
"\"Bucketeigenaar voorkeur\"."

#: sunshine-cloud-storage/includes/hooks.php:353
msgid ""
"<strong>How to fix:</strong> Check your storage provider's documentation for "
"enabling per-object ACLs on your bucket."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Oplossing:</strong> raadpleeg de documentatie van uw opslagprovider "
"voor het inschakelen van ACL's per object op uw bucket."

#: sunshine-cloud-storage/includes/hooks.php:357
msgid ""
